embeds.title: Old versions of BEE2 had a lot more items, what happened to them and are they coming back?
embeds.description: BEE2.4 is a complete rewrite of the app with a different internal item format, so all of the old items need to be manually ported. This is in progress, see issue [#95](https://github.com/BEEmod/BEE2-items/issues/95) for more details.
